description:
The following partial dataset&nbsp;is provided&nbsp;by the authors for&nbsp;the Quantitative Precipitation Estimation method presented in the paper. 

 wissdom_out_Taiwan_mosaic_202105010000.bin is wind data, the number means year, data, and time. 

 CAPPI_COMP_DR_202005100000.bin is radar data. 

 qpepre_202005010000-202005010100_1_h.txt is rain data. 

